<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>로그인</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/login.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="container page">
        <section class="login-wrap">
            <div class="login-box">
                <p class="login-label">ACCOUNT</p>
                <h2 class="login-title">로그인</h2>
                <p class="login-desc">아이디와 비밀번호를 입력해 로그인하세요.</p>

                <form class="login-form" id="login-form">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="login-id">아이디</label>
                        <input type="text" id="login-id" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요." />
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="login-password">비밀번호</label>
                        <input type="password" id="login-password" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요." />
                    </div>

                    <label class="login-remember-row" for="login-remember">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="login-remember" />
                        <span>로그인 상태 유지</span>
                    </label>

                    <p class="login-error" id="login-error"></p>

                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary login-submit">로그인</button>
                </form>

                <div class="auth-divider">
                    <span>또는</span>
                </div>

                <a href="/auth/google" class="btn btn-outline social-auth-btn google-auth-btn">
                    <img src="https://pvince-repository-production.up.railway.app/images/google.svg" alt="Google" />Google로 로그인
                </a>

                <div class="login-links">
                    <a href="/register-page">회원가입</a>
                    <a href="/forgot-password-page">비밀번호 찾기</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="login-side">
                <div class="login-side-card">
                    <p class="login-side-label">WELCOME</p>
                    <h3>템플릿을 구매하고<br />내 상품을 편하게 관리해보세요</h3>
                    <p>로그인하면 구매 내역 확인, 다운로드, 주문 관리 등 다양한 기능을 이용할 수 있습니다.</p>
                    <a href="/products-page" class="btn btn-outline">상품 보러가기</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/login.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/common.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
